606
00:30:13.286 --> 00:30:15.953
[Dog barking in distance]

607
00:30:15.955 --> 00:30:18.186
[Floorboards creaking]

608
00:30:18.197 --> 00:30:19.803
Ignacio?

609
00:30:19.814 --> 00:30:21.631
- _
- [Chuckles]

610
00:30:23.366 --> 00:30:25.683
_

611
00:30:25.694 --> 00:30:27.465
- [Chuckles]
- _

